==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Moulder
<hw>Mould"er</hw>, }</mhw> <pos>v. t.</pos>
<def>To turn to dust; to cause to crumble; to cause to waste
away.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[Time's] gradual touch⟦br⟧
Has <qex>moldered</qex> into beauty many a tower.</q>
<rj><qau>Mason.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

